{
  "texts": [
    "h, As in f, but for models trained on molecules from the GDB-13 database (all p ≤ 4.5 × 10 -10).",
    "i, As in e, but for models trained on sets of molecules with decreasing chemical diversity, as quantified by the minimum Tanimoto coefficient (Tc) from the seed molecule (all p ≤ 1.1 × 10 -12).",
    "j, As in f, but for models trained on sets of molecules with decreasing chemical diversity (all p ≤ 4.3 × 10 -9).",
    "k, As in e, but for models trained with data augmentation by non-canonical SMILES or SELFIES enumeration (all p ≤ 1.2 × 10 -13).",
    "l, As in f, but for models trained with data augmentation by non-canonical SMILES or SELFIES enumeration (all p ≤ 4.3 × 10 -10)."
  ]
